data.title: City Life Church
data.meta_description: City Life Church Chilliwack strives to help people Know God, Find Freedom, Discover Purpose, and Make a Difference
data.text:
This is God’s desire for you, and He’s working right now to accomplish this in your life! You are alive for a purpose, and it is our delight to join God’s mission in seeing this become a reality in you!

We've got an exciting summer coming up! Here are some of the key events to mark on your calendars:

Kids Camp: July 8-12

Youth Camp: August 18-22

Registration eligibility starts for those who finished Grade 7 this year
